An implementation of the model object 'Perspective'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Label
  • Icon URI
  • Tooltip
  • Localized Label
  • Localized Tooltip
  • Context
  • Variables
  • Properties
  • Handlers
  • Binding Contexts
